1. install docker

2. download git, clone the project

3. Build the docker images:  PROJECT_FOLDER/build.sh

4. Confirm images are created: docker images

5. start a selenium hub container: start_grid.sh

6. verify the grid at: http://host:4444/grid/console

7. Add Firefox, Phantom.js nodes to it: add_firefox_node.sh  add_phantomjs_node.sh

8. Verify the nodes are attached to the hub

9. Play with it

10. stop nodes: remove_all_firefox_nodes.sh   remove_all_phantomjs_nodes.sh

11. stop grid: stop_grid.sh
